     *Since:* 3.4.2

gnutls_pkcs7_get_crt_count
--------------------------

 -- Function: int gnutls_pkcs7_get_crt_count (gnutls_pkcs7_t PKCS7)
     PKCS7: should contain a 'gnutls_pkcs7_t' type

     This function will return the number of certifcates in the PKCS7 or
