gnutls_pkcs7_import
-------------------

 -- Function: int gnutls_pkcs7_import (gnutls_pkcs7_t PKCS7, const
          gnutls_datum_t * DATA, gnutls_x509_crt_fmt_t FORMAT)
     PKCS7: The data to store the parsed PKCS7.

